title: Morning Joe 4/14/21
description: Individuals protesting the police shooting of Daunte Wright took to the streets again in Brooklyn Center, Minn. on Tuesday night. And Kim Potter, the officer who fatally shot Wright, resigned Tuesday. The Morning Joe panel discusses.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
